attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Indulge in the epitome of luxury with this new construction penthouse boasting panoramic city views. This meticulously crafted 3-bed, 2 bath duplex exudes sophistication at every turn. Revel in the exquisite open-concept living space, stunning herringbone hardwood floors, custom Pella windows, and a gas fireplace with an integrated entertainment center. Seamless smart home integration enhances convenience, while the designer kitchen is a chef’s dream, equipped with top-of-the-line Fisher-Paykel paneled appliances including a wine fridge and an oversized island with quartz countertops and backsplash. Two guest bedrooms, a relaxing deck, and a contemporary bath complete the main level. The sun-drenched master suite on the second level offers a second spacious deck with a gas fireplace, bath with heated floors, and a wifi-enabled steam shower. Enjoy an entertainment room fully equipped with a wet bar with multiple beverage centers, and a third breathtaking outdoor space.
